- [Operational] 1 critical execution error(s), led by: Prompt validation hit an unsafe reflection path.

## 4. Action Hints

Compact next-step guidance derived from the highest-signal evidence in this run.

- [Spec] Protocol: Echo the negotiated protocol version in initialize.result.
- [Heuristic] Security: Sanitize and label untrusted content before returning it.
- [Guideline/Skip] prompts/list was skipped: Server does not advertise prompts capability.
- Add destructive hints to write-capable tools.

